      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The exterior remains clean and presentable, showing only minor signs of regular road use such as a few light stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is well-kept and comfortable, with all features functioning as they should. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
