    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen in the pre-owned market. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from its original showroom state, this is an investment-grade acquisition for the most demanding enthusiast.",
